topic: Book Workflow Series ("Nobel laureates explorative search")

goals.1: Identify the BGP for obtaining the nobel laureates and the nominees with their relevant attributes
goals.2: Get the number of Italian, French and Iranian winners and check which nation won more awards in the last twenty years.
goals.3: Determine how many Literature nobel laureates have the following contries: Italy, Germany, France, Romania, Denmark, Iran, and China
goals.4: How many Literature Nobel award winners have a PhD (aka Doctorate of Philosophy) (you may check if they have a doctoral advisor)?
goals.5: Are there books from Litarature Nobel Award winners which are not present in the Vatican Library? (if so, who is the author with more books not in the Vatical Library)?
